						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Tribhuvanachchakkravartti Vīrarājēndrachōḷa Year 4, <hi rend="italic">Makara</hi>, śu. di 10, Monday, <hi rend="italic">Aviṭṭam</hi> = 1278 A.D. Other details do not match.</hi></p>						

						<p>Incomplete. This epigraph records that Aviravāṉṉi Perumāḷ Selvaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Tiruvaraṅgadāṉaṉ, a merchant of Pūvirundavalli-nagaram made a gift of twilight lamp to the god Nīrvaṇṇaṉ of Tirunīrmalai. Other details are lost.</p>						

